# Nexus Tech Stack
- Core: React 19, TypeScript, Vite.
- Offline/PWA Orchestration: vite-plugin-pwa utilizing the InjectManifest strategy.
- Authentication: Google Identity Services (GIS) with Authorization Code Flow + PKCE.
- Data Layer: Native Google Sheets API (v4) & Google Drive API (v3).
- State Management: Zustand (offline cache) and React Query.

# Conventions
- Use strict TypeScript.
- Favor functional components and hooks.
- Apply the "Concise Architect" rule: Do not explain every single import; be concise.